{"tid":1037377,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Oppo 展示最新可摺疊手機　外貌激似華為 Mate X","createTime":"2019-02-26T01:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T05:36:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"51aaf27d84175cdcef5bf3890bb1249c33a2da05","tid":1037377,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:55:01.000Z","msg":"就在華為公佈最新可摺疊智能手機 Huawei Mate X 之際，同樣來自中國的手機生產商 Oppo 亦展示了他們的最新摺疊式熒幕手機。這部新機樣貌與 Mate X 極為相似，未知在價格上能否擊敗同國籍售價超過 2 萬港元的 Mate X 呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z1nn11f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1nn11f.png&h=6cce0fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j3mcENW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3mcENW.png&h=82911be4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PAcWm1g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPAcWm1g.png&h=a607bbd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOppo 副總裁沈義人在個人微博上發出帖文，展示了他們新一代摺疊式熒幕手機產品。雖然它只是一部樣本機，但可見其設計與剛剛在 MWC 2019 展覽中發佈的華為 Mate X 樣貌相當似。<br />\n<br />\n對於這方面，沈義人否認此機使用公模，表示這些硬件都是自己研發。另一方面他也提到，Samsung Galaxy Fold 的內摺疊式設計，會令到手機變得非常厚，使用上也不方便，所以他們會用到外摺疊式的設計。<br />\n<br />\n由於連產品都未正式發佈，我們也很難清楚它的實際售價，但對於歐洲賣價 2299 歐元（約港幣HK$20,416）的 Huawei Mate X 以及售價 1,980 美元的 Samsung Galaxy Fold（約港幣HK$15,538）超高售價摺疊式手機來說，能否在價格上取得優勢，就要期待他們進一步發佈了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/02/25/oppofoldablephone/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F02%2F25%2Foppofoldablephone%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfWztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=46815297\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/02/25/oppofoldablephone/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"632fa1926f0a5b295c0a5db374fb2e4e4a0cb7c7","tid":1037377,"uid":78166,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:59:58.000Z","msg":"抄嚟抄去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n